import React from 'react' import './Internal.css' const AboutMe = () => { return (

Welcome!


A little about myself.

I am a detail-oriented college student currently attending College of Southern Nevada in Las Vegas for Computing & Information Technology and in the process of receiving my certification in Full-Stack Software Engineering through a 600+ hour course at Flatiron School.

During the course of my academic career, I also managed to accrue nearly 6 years of work experience.

Most recently, I have had the privilege of working for Lopez Brothers as an Automotive Technician Assistant, where I learned valuable professional skills such as customer needs assessment, record management, and workflow planning.
); }; export default AboutMe;
